{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/cli-clipboardy","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a468ec54-a075-5d19-96c4-d26d9ba9ecb7","html":"<p>This is a series of libraries and utilities for building Command-line-interfaces aka CLI using Node.js and ecosystem around it. Similar utilities/helpers may be available for other languages but, these series is focused on JavaScript and its friends.</p>\n<p>You can check all articles under <a href=\"/category/cli-build-tool/\"><code class=\"language-text\">CLI Build Tool</code></a> tag.</p>\n<h2 id=\"clipboardy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clipboardy\" aria-label=\"clipboardy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/clipboardy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">clipboardy</a></h2>\n<p>If you are building a CLI and need to access the system clipboard, <code class=\"language-text\">clipboardy</code> is the package you need. Of course, it is cross-platform and supports macOS, Windows, Linux, OpenBSD, FreeBSD, Android with Termux.</p>\n<p>It provides APIs in both variants , async (Promise) and sync.\n<code class=\"language-text\">clipboardy</code> has a very easy to follow, simple to use API. Here is a code example:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> clipboardy <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'clipboardy'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ns<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nclipboardy<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">writeSync</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'something to copy to clipboard'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nclipboardy<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">readSync</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// read from clipboard</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can check out official <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/clipboardy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">repo</a> for all usage details.</p>\n<p>Github Repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/clipboardy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">clipboardy</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"related\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#related\" aria-label=\"related permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Check <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/clipboardy-cli\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">clipboardy-cli</a> - CLI version for this module</li>\n<li>Check <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/copy-text-to-clipboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">copy-text-to-clipboard</a> for browser version</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/cli-clipboardy","tagSlugs":["/tag/cli/","/tag/tools/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-01T18:05:00.738Z","description":"Node.js CLI App helper for working on clipboard","tags":["CLI","Tools"],"title":"Tool of the Trade for CLI Apps - `clipboardy`  ðŸ“‹","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/cli-clipboardy"}}}